The '''Newlincs EfW facility''' is an [[incinerator]] which is located in [[Grimsby]], [[North East Lincolnshire]], England. The plant is operated by Cyclerval UK & TIRU Group under a [[Private Finance Initiative|PFI]] contract. The engineering of the facility is unusual as it consists of an oscillating kiln handling 56,000 tonnes of [[waste]] per year/7 tonnes per hour of waste. The facility is capable of generating 3.2&nbsp;MW electricity.<ref>[http://www.newlincs.com/tiru_group_ref_plants.pdf Your Energy Your Waste], www.newlincs.com, Retrieved 22 February 2007</ref>

